This repository contains structured study material from the *Total Data Visualization Techniques* textbook, organized in a unit-wise and topic-wise format for easier access and understanding. Relevant sections of the textbook have been carefully cropped and compiled into separate PDF files according to the syllabus topics. This organization helps students quickly locate specific concepts without navigating through the entire book, making it useful for efficient learning, quick revision, and exam preparation in the field of Data Visualization.
